lead_paragraph: KRAININ--Bette Finley, died peacefully June 16 at home in Kailua, Hawaii. Born in Maine, was a successful model, married photographer Ewing Krainin (deceased) and travelled the world. Their loving daughter Cameron survives her. 1/3
